[{"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "渴望被愛的慟哭　前篇", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "吶……看著我吧。認同我吧。愛我吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "但那些是不可能的。因為，我什麼都沒有，無論力量還是才能。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我有三位哥哥。三哥普羅米修斯相當傲慢。明明自己擁有「原初之炎」，卻憐憫無能的我而常搭理我。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "和他相比，阿特拉斯兄長大人以及墨諾提俄斯哥哥就優秀得多。擁有無比強大的力量！強大又睿智，並且充滿傲氣。和我根本是天壤之別。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "所以我才不被兄長大人他們所愛。沒有誰會愛路邊的碎石吧。和那是一樣的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "能被愛的生命，在出生時早已注定。不被愛的生命亦同。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我原本是這麼想的……但那天不同。因為我聽見了。阿特拉斯兄長大人和墨諾提俄斯哥哥正在談論我的事。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "兄長大人們的世界裡，我是確實存在著的！深沉的漆黑中，射入了一道光芒。──直到我聽見兄長們的談話。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「艾比米修斯沒有什麼變化吧？」「嗯，還是跟我們奪走那股不祥的力量時一樣。」", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "咦……？兄長們，奪走了我的力量？兄長們，到底在說什麼呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我會這麼無能，是兄長他們害的……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "為什麼？我做了什麼？不明白。總覺得一切都無法理解。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "任何人都好。誰來、誰來告訴我是誤會。對了，如果是那傢伙，如果是會理睬無能的我、那個好事的傢伙一定──！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 210112011, "title": "渴望被愛的慟哭　前篇"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "渴望被愛的慟哭　後篇", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "不被愛是因為無能，無能的我不會被愛。我會如此無能，是因為被兄長們奪走了力量？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "騙人的，這一定有什麼誤會。對了。如果是會搭理我的那傢伙，一定知道真相才對──！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「普羅米修斯，快告訴我。奪走我力量的是兄長大人他們嗎？你早就知道這件事了嗎？」", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "事到如此是憐憫還是什麼都好，求求你，告訴我那是誤會。只有你曾經試著愛我對吧……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「你在哪裡聽到的？那是只有我們才知道的事。」", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "啊啊，原來是這樣。連你也，騙了我啊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "不原諒你。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "不原諒你不原諒你不原諒你不原諒你不原諒你不原諒你不原諒你不原諒你不原諒你不原諒你不原諒你不原諒你不原諒你不原諒你不原諒你不原諒你不原諒你不原諒你不原諒你……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "無法停止滿溢的哀怨。也無法給予組織語言的慈悲。想將一切破壞殆盡。只專注著，將憎怨累積於兩手之中。然後──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我的半身，被「原初之炎」所燒灼。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "雖然他似乎說了些什麼，但我腦中只想從這裡消失，於是我甩開了他的手。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "好痛、好痛、好痛。啊啊……該怎麼做我才能被愛呢？兄長他們，就那麼討厭我的力量嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "沒錯……一定是這樣。既然如此，只要生出其他力量就好了嗎？嗯，一定是這樣的！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "嫉妒、憎惡、絕望……全部、全部，都化為我力量的糧食！這是……這就是我新的力量，終於得到的被愛資格！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "吶，兄長大人……看著我吧。我得到新的力量了，是很棒的力量喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "吶……為什麼又要離開我？我擁有力量，是件那麼糟糕的事嗎？等等，兄長大人、哥哥，別走。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "吶……求求你們。愛我。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 210112012, "title": "渴望被愛的慟哭　後篇"}]